anization)|The South Centre]]<ref name=nkintheworld/>\n* [[United Nations]]<ref name=cia/>\n* [[United Nations Children's Fund]] (UNICEF)<ref name=nkintheworld/>\n* [[United Nations Conference on Trade and Development]]<ref name=cia/>\n* [[United Nations Development Fund for Women]]<ref name=nkintheworld/>\n* [[United Nations Development Programme]]<ref name=nkintheworld>{{Cite web |title=International Organizations |publisher=East-West Center, The National Committee on North Korea |work=North Korea in the World |date=May 22, 2016 |access-date=February 24, 2019 |url=https://www.northkoreaintheworld.org/multilateral/international-organizations |archive-date=February 24, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190224231623/https://www.northkoreaintheworld.org/multilateral/international-organizations |url-status=live }}</ref>\n* [[United Nations Economic and Social Commission for Asia and the Pacific]]<ref name=nkintheworld/>\n* [[United Nations Educational, Scientific, and Cultural Organization]] (UNESCO)<ref name=cia/>\n* [[United Nations Environment Programme]]<ref name=nkintheworld/>\n* [[United Nations Industrial Development Organization]]<ref name=cia/>\n* [[United Nations Population Fund]]<ref name=nkintheworld/>\n* [[World Tourism Organization]]<ref name=cia/>\n* [[Universal Postal Union]]<ref name=cia/>\n* [[World Federation of Trade Unions]]<ref name=cia/>\n* [[World Food Programme]]<ref name=nkintheworld/>\n* [[World Health Organization]]<ref name=cia/>\n* [[World Intellectual Property Organization]]<ref name=cia/>\n* [[World Meteorological Organization]]<ref name=cia/>\n* [[World Organisation for Animal Health]]<ref name=nkintheworld/>\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Notable people==\n<!---♦♦♦ Only add a person to this list if they already have their own article on the English Wikipedia ♦♦♦--->\n<!---♦♦♦ Please keep the list in alphabetical order by LAST NAME ♦♦♦--->\n* [[Pak Tong-chun]], diplomat\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|North Korea|Politics}}\n* [[List of 